Use Cases for CoCo

teacher point of view:
	upload, re-upload (files or whole folder)
	delete (files or whole folder)
	create folder	
	comments on folders (editional information for the course)
	
public point of view:
	browse folder hierarchy
	find-as-you-type-search for materials and comments
	comments on files
	download files and folders
	facebook-like-button
	
	
functions for the future:
	rights management for folders and files
